These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, jazz, classical, trance
1. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
3. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | soul | jazz | classical | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | december | july | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, broccoli, corn, cranberry
1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | pineapple | corn | broccoli | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, sprite, lemonade
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk | lemonade | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
