2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Birthday   | april | december | january | october |

