1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Pet   | mouse | frog | dog | bird |

