3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | water | milk | almond-milk |

