.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Transport   | jet-ski | bus | helicopter | boat |

 